column2: "Uh... where is this... where... did I come from?"
"You came at a good time peon. Ah hey, you peon. Hey peon! Look over here!"
"Hey peon. Where are you going? No! Which way did you come? Where is this? Hey peon, answer me!"
"These directions are really easy to understand. I praise you for not sucking, peon."
"Lost? Who? Me? ... Like that would happen peon!"
"Lost kid? Ha! The reason I was asking was to make sure you weren't completely incompetent!"
"Now I'm pissed. Get out of the way peon, I'm going home."
